OL,3,C'Sadistic' British crocodile expert
OL,4,Cjailed for sexually abusing dogs
OL,6,FWarning: This story contains
OL,7,Fdistressing details
OL,9,FA "sadistic" British zoologist has
OL,10,Fbeen jailed in Australia after
OL,11,Fadmitting raping, torturing and
OL,12,Fkilling dozens of dogs.
OL,14,FAdam Britton, originally from West
OL,15,FYorkshire, abused more than 42 dogs in
OL,16,Fa shipping container on his rural
OL,17,Fproperty until almost all of them died.
