OL,3,C'Sadistic' British crocodile expert
OL,4,Cjailed for sexually abusing dogs
OL,6,FThe 53-year-old, who was based in
OL,7,FDarwin, Australia, also pleaded guilty
OL,8,Fto four counts of accessing and
OL,9,Ftransmitting child abuse material.
OL,11,FThe Northern Territory Supreme Court
OL,12,Fheard he filmed and shared videos of
OL,13,Fhimself abusing the animals online.
OL,15,FThe offences spanned years and went
OL,16,Funnoticed, until a clue was spotted in
OL,17,Fone of his videos.
OL,19,FThe court previously heard he had a
OL,20,F"sadistic sexual interest" in animals.
