OL,3,C'Sadistic' British crocodile expert
OL,4,Cjailed for sexually abusing dogs
OL,6,FChief Justice Michael Grant described
OL,7,FBritton's "grotesque" crimes against
OL,8,Fanimals as he sentenced him.
OL,10,FHe warned the gallery that details of
OL,11,Fthe "devious" offences could cause a
OL,12,F"nervous shock or some other adverse
OL,13,Fpsychological reactions".
OL,15,FAs the facts of the case were read
OL,16,Fout, some members of the public left
OL,17,Fthe building.
