OL,3,C'Sadistic' British crocodile expert
OL,4,Cjailed for sexually abusing dogs
OL,6,FJustice Grant said the renowned
OL,7,Fcrocodile expert's "depravity" fell
OL,8,Fentirely outside any ordinary human
OL,9,Fconception.
OL,11,FBritton attended Queen Elizabeth
OL,12,FGrammar School in Wakefield, and
OL,13,Fgraduated with a Zoology degree from
OL,14,FLeeds University.
OL,16,FIn 1996, he moved to Australia and
OL,17,Fearned a global reputation for his
OL,18,Fexpertise. He had worked for the BBC
OL,19,Fas a crocodile expert with David
OL,20,FAttenborough as well as with National
OL,21,FGeographic.
