OL,3,C'Sadistic' British crocodile expert
OL,4,Cjailed for sexually abusing dogs
OL,6,FHe apologised for his "demeaning
OL,7,Fcrimes" in a letter in court.
OL,9,FHe said: "I deeply regret the pain and
OL,10,Ftrauma that I caused to innocent
OL,11,Fanimals and consequently to my family,
OL,12,Ffriends and members of the community."
OL,14,FHe pleaded guilty to 56 charges of
OL,15,Fbestiality and animal cruelty and was
OL,16,Fjailed for ten years and five months.
OL,18,FHe was also banned from owning any
OL,19,Fmammals for the rest of his life.
